 <span data-ttu-id="69d15-114">Le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> pour une expression est obtenue à l’aide de l’instance la <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A> propriété sur le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> objet (ou des objets qui héritent de celui-ci, telles que <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult>).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69d15-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance for a phrase is obtained using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> object (or objects that inherit from it, such as <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult>).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="69d15-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> objets obtenus des expressions reconnues sans structure sémantique sont caractérisés par :</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69d15-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> objects obtained for recognized phrases without semantic structure are characterized by:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="69d15-116">L’absence d’enfants (<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Count%2A> est 0).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69d15-116">The lack of children (<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Count%2A> is 0).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="69d15-117">La propriété <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> a la valeur `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69d15-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property is `null`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="69d15-118">Un niveau de confiance de sémantique artificiel 1.0 (retourné par <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69d15-118">An artificial semantic confidence level of 1.0 (returned by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span></span>  
  
